{"tid":2029621,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【国安法】其實有無人諗過，国安法係共產党用嚟治班黑狗？","createTime":"2020-05-22T10:19:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-22T10:26:31.000Z","uid":54337,"like":1,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"8d7711bbd88ba0ff5c607f109a6aeac62f0ab794","tid":2029621,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T10:19:01.000Z","msg":"不嬲都係党指揮槍<br />\n但班黑狗有槍在身，張建宗都敢反。<br />\n張好好睇睇都係共產党直接任命嘅特區官員<br />\n黑狗此舉係槍指揮党<br />\n係共產党心入面嘅大諱大忌<br />\n<br />\n有無人諗過係共產党忍緊班狗，所以時辰到，決定郁手？"},{"pid":"20b8c91a89daa7bf071a938e84dbb38f63e85f46","tid":2029621,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T10:20:20.000Z","msg":"鄧竟成：特區需制定具體政策決定國安法是否由警隊執行<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2029508\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2029508</a><br />\n<br />\n鄧已經聞到陣除，所以即刻出聲問清楚"},{"pid":"f436f5cbeb0603721340feab40314352999ba32c","tid":2029621,"uid":58552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T10:20:58.000Z","msg":"擺明唔係"},{"pid":"bdf727c773ae465b0d0df9f083174b459cd86684","tid":2029621,"uid":189157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T10:21:41.000Z","msg":"冇<br />\n共產黨都有好人<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>拉</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"dccfff37f71b724a07ad5e36cbe12b92b9d16b26","tid":2029621,"uid":214173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T10:22:23.000Z","msg":"我唔理,總之我反國安法<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"933159005e2bd7a1f7615b4fe0b90b234ab143f8","tid":2029621,"uid":59570,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T10:23:28.000Z","msg":"On9就讀多幾年書啦"},{"pid":"2fecfda5ef401c02f0f6a82c0b03cc237961c75d","tid":2029621,"uid":146621,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T10:26:31.000Z","msg":"樓豬5毛<br />\n講緊國安法<br />\n咁都想洗白<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"h